################### SECURING JENKINS #################
1.username & passwords are stored in jenkins by deflaut
*dashboard - manage jenkins - configure global security - security realm

2.new user created in jenkins by admin
*dashboard - manage jenkins - manage users - creat new user

3.matrix based security
*dashboard - manage jenkins - configure global security - authorization
*using this we can configure granual level of permission to jenkins user

4.Project-based Matrix Authorization Strategy
*NOT GIVE TICKS TO JOB
*dashboard - manage jenkins - configure global security - authorization
*this is extension of matrix based security & offers job level access
